 <h2>Why did I develop duplicate tab extension?</h2>
 <h3>Android Firefox does not have this button, which is inconvenient.</h3>
 <p>
 Originally, if you want to copy a tab, you need to copy the URL and paste it to the new tab, which is very troublesome. So I developed the <a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/duplicate-tab-for-fx-mobile/">duplicate tab extension</a> , which allows you to duplicate tabs by just clicking the duplicate tab button. Later I integrated it to <a href="index.html">Show Close Tab Button</a>.
</p>
